headline: Boot Barn, Zumiez, Williams-Sonoma, and Academy Sports Shares Are Soaring, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks jumped in the afternoon session after the White House announced a one-year delay on planned tariff hikes for many home goods, including furniture and cabinets.
